Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.44,0:00:07.65,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I heard from Mr. Rizzo that\Nthe chef here is quite talented.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.94,0:00:13.65,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.65,0:00:16.32,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,This is tonight's\Nantipasto misto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:27.21,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Please take your\Ntime to savor it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:30.00,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,See? It looks delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:31.13,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:51.36,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:53.36,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:53.94,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Waiter!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.45,0:00:55.40,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:01:02.66,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Why do all the employees\Nhere wear spectacles?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:05.54,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Well, that's this\Nrestaurant's trademark.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:06.42,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.83,0:01:13.42,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,This mysterious restaurant is on a road just a little ways from the center of Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:54.57,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:58.94,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Oh, those are photographs taken when this restaurant opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:03.24,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,The staff has changed\Na little since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:06.04,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,That man wasn't\Nwearing spectacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:08.16,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Yes, that's why he left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:10.08,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Wait, he was fired?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:13.08,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Of course not.\NThat's not grounds for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:16.05,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,But the owner\Nis a curious one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:19.97,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,It's one thing to have a wife who likes bespectacled gentlemen, it's another to open a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:24.72,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Well, anyway, this wine\Nis truly delectable, Gigi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:29.31,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,He treats his wife\Nlike a goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:31.94,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,She truly met a wonderful man to make her husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:35.44,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,Look at her,\Nsmiling like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:37.48,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Are you not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:39.82,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:42.11,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Feel free to speak your\Nmind about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:47.45,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,If you're a friend of the Madam,\Nyou're a friend of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:51.12,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NI will do just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:58.00,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,Man... Now I can't tell them\NI'm really her daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:02.63,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's really\Ncomfortable living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:05.72,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She's taking care of all\Nmy living expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:09.72,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Though she did break her\Npromise to meet and talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:12.77,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Well, she is really busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:19.40,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Hey, Grandma...\NThere's a guy I really like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:23.15,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,But I can't tell if\Nit's love or what...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:27.24,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I'm not really good at talking about these sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:28.91,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Why don't you talk to Olga?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.66,0:04:33.75,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She's your mother, plus you're all the way there, in Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:41.30,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,My grandmother was the one who suggested I go to Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:45.97,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,I know it's because she wanted me to make up with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:49.35,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,I get that she's busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:52.64,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,Well, if I'm staying\Nhere in Rome,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:55.19,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,I should probably\Nlook for a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:05.74,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,But, what sort of job\Nshould I look for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:09.07,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,I just moved here without\Nthinking things through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:19.63,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,They're closed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.88,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:32.60,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Shall we go get\Nsome food, Francesco?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:34.98,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Sure, Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:36.89,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,How about\Nthat panini place?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:39.40,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I wonder if they\Nhave my usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:40.40,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:42.02,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:48.70,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:52.24,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:05:57.71,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Luciano!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:06:00.71,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Nonno, who's she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:03.09,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,She's a friend of\Nthe owner's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:07.63,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,For some reason, she's been coming to eat with the staff every day at the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:11.14,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Your grandson?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:16.39,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I'm Francesco.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:17.89,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:21.81,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I'm Nicoletta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:24.78,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Don't believe everything your grandfather says about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:27.36,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:29.41,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Gigi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:31.24,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Buon giorno.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:36.25,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Are you always\Non this bench?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:41.42,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Sheesh... Why can't they just let me relax on my day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:53.68,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Put that all in, too.\NWe'll add in salt and pepper.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:55.81,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You're good\Nat cooking, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:59.69,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,It's because I used to help my grandma cook since I was about your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:02.23,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Your grandma?\NNot your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:06.07,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,That's right. I learned how to cook from my grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:07.57,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:14.16,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Buono!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:17.20,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Well? Change your\Nmind about me at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:19.75,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Not bad, for an amateur.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:21.00,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:22.33,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,He spoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:25.00,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,How long are you in town?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:27.96,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Planning to stay\Nin Rome forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:30.05,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I don't think I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:32.38,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,What do your parents\Nsay about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:36.93,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,My daddy's always\Ntaking business trips.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:39.48,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Oh, that must be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:42.31,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,In any case, look for a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:44.40,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You can't just\Nbe here for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.98,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You've got to\Ntake it seriously—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.98,0:07:48.98,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Save the speech,\NI'm already looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:50.24,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:51.99,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,{\an4}Don't copy me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:51.99,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Don't copy her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:53.36,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:01.37,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Claudio's not coming today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:09.80,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Maybe, since it's his day off, he's treating his wife and kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:10.71,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:13.93,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:17.39,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Wow, this pasta\Nis actually edible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:21.23,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:27.36,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Sounds like Nicoletta is spending a lot of time at the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:31.90,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You never know what to expect from her. She's still a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:34.40,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Why don't you invite\Nher over sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:36.91,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Since she's your\Nfriend and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:40.74,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,To be honest, I don't know\Nhow to connect to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:45.42,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,In my mind, she's still that little girl I knew years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:48.34,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Just treat her normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:50.84,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Don't worry so much.\NIt's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:52.76,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:02.98,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What's with Luciano?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:05.52,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,He treats me like a little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:13.69,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,Though it's true, I've never really thought about my future.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:21.87,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,I really should think\Nabout my future.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:27.54,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,But, for the time being,\Nlove is just as important!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:32.00,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Buon giorno, Nicoletta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:33.38,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Buon giorno.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:35.17,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Buon giorno.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:39.60,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,Is this love?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:43.22,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,I really don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:46.89,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:50.52,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,Like this Luciano guy who\Ndoes nothing but complain...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:55.49,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I'll walk you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.07,0:10:04.75,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,If he suddenly became really kind to me, would I fall in love with him over that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:15.09,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,They said it wasn't\Ngonna rain today...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:17.30,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Shall I call you a cab?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:19.09,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I'll be fine if I run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:22.55,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I'd be fine doing that, but you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:26.60,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Use it. You'll both fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:30.23,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:32.40,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Thank you, Luciano.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:34.23,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I'm loaning it to Claudio.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.23,0:10:36.44,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Now take her home before\Nthe sky really opens up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:42.24,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:43.53,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:53.09,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,That's true. Gigi is\Nsomewhat strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:57.21,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,But he's a good guy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:04.01,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What's your\Nwife like, Claudio?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:14.90,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I don't have one, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:18.90,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,But... that ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:22.41,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,There's a reason I wear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:27.91,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,There are some customers who try and pursue me for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:30.21,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,They'll start talking about\Nmarriage and the like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:33.92,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,So, this is a countermeasure\Nagainst that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:37.92,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,My wife and I\Nseparated years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:42.43,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:46.10,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,He opened up to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:06.62,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,I hate the whole\Nidea of adultery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:09.49,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,I'd never bring up the\Nidea of marriage, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:21.88,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,My wife and I\Nseparated years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:27.39,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,There are some customers who try and pursue me for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.80,0:12:31.22,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,So, this is a countermeasure\Nagainst that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:36.27,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:39.36,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Uh, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:40.40,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:42.40,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.94,0:12:44.82,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:46.91,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:51.83,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,This smells lovely.\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:54.37,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I bought it at a shop nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:12:58.21,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:12:59.75,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:01.84,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,I can't take my\Neyes off of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:08.97,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,He's so much older than I am... I've never felt like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:21.78,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:26.03,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I want to try and see\Nif this is all right or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.99,0:13:32.66,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I know I like you,\Nbut I can't tell if it's real...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:38.33,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Hold on a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:42.17,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:45.17,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I mustn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:56.31,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,I think... he's a real gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:13:59.60,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Nicoletta, it's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:01.52,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I brought you\Nsome chocolates!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:09.53,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Keep your hands\Noff my Claudio.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:11.28,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Why's he yours?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:14.58,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,All the gentlemen\Nthere belong to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:19.96,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I'm truly sorry for being in your friend's apartment at such a late hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:22.21,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,It's fine. Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:26.17,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I know that she dragged\Nyou here against your will.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:27.84,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:30.84,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I'll let the two of you talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:33.18,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Ah... All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:36.85,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You're not serious, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:41.94,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You're serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:44.77,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm single,\Nso who cares!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:48.15,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Then why not go\Nafter Luciano? He's single!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:49.32,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:50.99,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Then, Teo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:54.87,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What is this? It's like you don't want me going after Claudio for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:15:01.50,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Well... I understand, but Claudio doesn't know how to handle a woman's advances.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:04.88,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Say, why don't you move back to your grandmother's?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:06.63,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:10.13,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You're young. There's no\Nneed to rush things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:13.39,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You should focus on\Ngetting a job, and your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:17.77,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Enough! Why does everyone treat me like a little kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:18.73,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:20.69,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I've thought about\Nall that already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:23.27,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,But I don't know\Nwhat I should do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:25.40,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I don't know\Nwhat I'd be good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:28.74,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You're good\Nat cooking, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:36.95,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Hey, why'd you go\Nquiet all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:39.25,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Hey, I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:40.12,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:45.84,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,If you help me out, I'll reconsider telling your husband that I'm your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:57.68,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I'm Nicoletta and I'll be working as an apprentice here, starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:15:59.18,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I look forward to\Nworking with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:01.23,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Since Lorenzo\Nsaid it was fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:02.81,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,it's OK with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:07.07,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,But promise me you\Nwon't leave the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:09.07,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:19.16,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,So you've always had\Nan interest in cooking, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:21.83,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,They said you even went\Nto cooking school for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:26.63,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Yes, but I had never\Nthought about it as a career.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:29.59,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,So what made you\Nchange your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:32.22,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I couldn't figure out\Nwhat I wanted to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:34.13,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,but I knew I wanted\Nto be independent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:38.64,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I plan on using this opportunity to learn everything I can about cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:40.14,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:43.39,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Say, you give cooking classes at your home, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:45.35,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Can I join in?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:47.11,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I'd love that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:50.03,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Man, there's no pancetta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:53.03,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Giuseppe swore up and\Ndown he'd get it, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:57.57,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,That's no good. We can call,\Nbut it takes them a while to deliver it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:16:59.99,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,How about I go and get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:02.45,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Just tell me where to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:07.17,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Claudio. You heard her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:09.09,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Please escort her there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:24.35,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:27.44,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Sorry about last night,\Nfor doing that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:33.69,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,But, I want to let you\Nknow that I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:35.03,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I don't regret what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:43.58,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,It's fine. I'll lay off a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:46.33,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Nicoletta, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:49.33,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I'm serious about\Nlearning how to cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.33,0:17:54.59,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I didn't start working at the restaurant just because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:58.72,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I want to try and pursue something I may be good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:00.85,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I don't want to\Nalways depend on Olga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:04.60,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I want to be truly\Nindependent someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:09.02,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Then, I'll become a great woman,\Nand get back at {\i1}her{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:12.65,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I've had enough of people\Ntreating me like a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:16.61,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Please give it your all.\NI'll support you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.61,0:18:19.61,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Sure. I can use your\Nsupport more than ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:27.12,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Ladies first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:28.16,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:35.84,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,It's so great to be working\Nin the same place as him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:39.47,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Gabrielle's coming tonight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:42.10,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I'll have to make\Na really grand dolce, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:46.68,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,Gabrielle? Could that\Nbe someone special?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:58.44,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Buonasera.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.99,0:19:01.78,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Gabrielle is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:02.95,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:06.20,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Hey, is Gabrielle\Na VIP or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:09.21,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Yes. She's Claudio's ex-wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:11.50,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I wanna see!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:13.21,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Stay out of sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:22.89,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,She has such beautiful skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:25.72,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,That's his ex-wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:26.85,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:30.73,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,Well, it is his "ex"-wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:39.69,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Good work today, Nicoletta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.69,0:19:40.82,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:52.79,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,When are you going to\Nstop wearing that ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:19:59.96,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I won't order you\Nto do it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:06.51,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Anyway, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:20.11,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I interrupted\Nyour conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:21.32,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Nothing of the sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:27.53,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,Claudio...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:32.29,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,Could he still have\Nfeelings for his ex-wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.96,0:20:42.34,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,The restaurant is located\Non a street in Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:45.64,Ristorante italic,FV,0,0,0,,Its name is casetta dell'orso.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.19,0:20:55.40,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She's my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.06,0:20:59.44,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:00.44,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,What?!
